{"tid":471522,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"港人壓力從細建立","createTime":"2017-11-17T10:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T16:09:57.000Z","uid":102642,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"228327f81ccc0237f76276b664c4288aeece8ddb","tid":471522,"uid":102642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"事源坐小巴聽到2個小學生放學傾計，港童發現外藉童冇帶一樣野返屋企，但我聽唔清楚咩野黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：港童<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：外藉童<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜你做咩唔帶返個野返屋企?唔怕比人罵咩?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：it's okay~你唔好問d咁傻既問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好小事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：如果比我冇帶實比媽咪daddy打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港人成日講大壓力，我覺得好多時都係因為好多小事會化到天咁大，港童因為小野而比人打罵，而外藉童屋企人唔會因為小事而比人話，仲反宜覺得因為為而樣野擔心係傻，覺得港人教育下一代真係教到好垃圾。到大個左，係香港返工老闆又會將好多小事而定好多無謂政策，加上工時，怪唔得咁多人抑鬱情緒病。<br />\n<br />\n到底港人係未同壓力已經不可分離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：垃圾"},{"pid":"434bab7353b6927cfc88d18da969cb8df813fa5a","tid":471522,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"教育同社會好有問題"},{"pid":"5474f58b94fe1e6d39e4167dfebe5ad9b6d287ea","tid":471522,"uid":88428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾上一代"},{"pid":"29eac9b5c0aa45522b6267126e8eb3511392f79f","tid":471522,"uid":102642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693cb28473ffebb6af97ac6c09e61be009eb52b0","tid":471522,"uid":60136,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:23:38.000Z","msg":"代代都話為左下一代 點知都係用盡權力同資源去鞏固自己(/自己個代)既地位 我想問 到底邊代先係下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e4626b66439a21994adff7c08e29a4ee55af31","tid":471522,"uid":102642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"我寧願唔升職都唔想死捱難捱用多過人生3分1時間去返工<br />\n可能人地覺得我怪唔上進（有2xk已經夠）<br />\n但我覺得果d人仲怪，死博難博（可能人工已經3xk去博4xk）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底我怪定人怪"},{"pid":"8ad3606fda179bf81406f3166303105b0d57d3fd","tid":471522,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:55:57.000Z","msg":"未讀幼稚園果陣已經要上補習，面試班<br />\n根本痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔知ed上親報既係極端例子定好普遍"},{"pid":"20d04abb8523bcccf435cc1dacb11d2fcc362d0c","tid":471522,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未讀幼稚園果陣已經要上補習，面試班<br />\n根本痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔知ed上親報既係極端例子定好普遍</blockquote><br />\n好多痴線家長,仲要越嚟越多,依家啲所謂學校唔係教育係搵錢"}]}